   630→    <div style="background: white; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 16px; text-align: center;">
   631→      <div class="spinner-large" style="width: 48px; height: 48px; border: 4px solid #eee; border-top-color: #667eea; border-radius: 50%; animation: spin 1s linear infinite; margin: 0 auto 1rem;"></div>
